	"https://github.com/Loyalsoldier/v2ray-rules-dat/releases/download/${pkgver}/geosite.dat")
sha256sums=('e04b9d4eb02cd78bed36d900317cdafdc0fa029dbfb641b07459fed2545ac987'
            '1cdfc2f4bfa925b96b2dde7625f789df70cd9ba730991ab8fc239b0056078703')

